<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>태양광 모니터링 - 발전량 예측</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.10.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.4.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/lib/animate/animate.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/lib/owlcarousel/assets/owl.carousel.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #6a11cb, #2575fc);
            color: #fff;
            font-family: 'Heebo', sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .navbar {
            background-color: #6a11cb;
            padding: 15px 0;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 20px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .navbar a {
            color: white;
            margin: 0 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .navbar .team-name {
            position: absolute;
            left: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .right-nav {
            position: absolute;
            right: 20px;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .logout-btn {
            margin-left: 15px;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border: 2px solid #17a2b8; /* 민트색 테두리 */
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
            background-color: #6a11cb; /* 네비게이션 바 색상 */
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .logout-btn:hover {
            background-color: #5c0db6; /* 마우스 오버 시 약간 더 어두운 색 */
        }

        .container {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            padding: 20px;
            width: 60%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            flex-direction: row;
        }

        .weather-info {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .weather-item {
            background-color: #17a2b8;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            flex-grow: 1;
            height: 50px;
            max-width: 300px;
            white-space: nowrap; /* 줄바꿈 방지 */
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .weather-item p {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .forecast-container {
            flex-grow: 2;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            border-radius: 10px;
            height: 300px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #333;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="navbar" style="position: relative;">
        <div class="team-name">ANS</div>
        <a href="/dashboard">발전량 통계</a>
        <a href="/forecast">발전량 예측</a>
        <a href="/mode">모드</a>
        <a href="/trade">전력 거래</a>
        <a href="/news">기술 소식</a>
    
        <div class="right-nav">
            <span><%= userNickname %>님 환영합니다!</span>
            <a href="/user/logout" class="logout-btn">로그아웃</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    

    <div class="container">
        <div class="weather-info">
            <div class="weather-item">
                <p>기온: <%= temperature %></p>
            </div>
            <div class="weather-item">
                <p>날씨: <%= weather %></p>
            </div>
            <div class="weather-item">
                <p>강수확률: <%= rainProbability %></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="forecast-container">
            예측 그래프
        </div>
    </div>    
</body>
</html>
